      <div class="widget-item">
       <h3 class="widget-title">
        Who We Are
       </h3>
       <p>
        SCKOPEMATE KONSULT  LIMITED, with registration  number RC995344, was established and being operated by a team of experienced,  specialized and multi-disciplined professionals, to provide strategic and wide  range of services in the oil &amp; gas, energy, power, engineering, construction  and public sectors of the economy.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        Our emphasis has been geared towards establishing  mutually satisfying relationship with our clients, while performing either as Consultants,  Engineers, Contractors or Project Managers.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        We take pride in our West African regional knowledge in  both Francophone and Anglophone countries to provide a unique range of  services, organized in three categories:- Geomatics, Environmental, Engineering and  Construction.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        Visit our website for  more detailed description of our services:
        <u>
         <a href="http://www.sckope.com/">
          www.sckope.com
         </a>
        </u>
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <div class="sample-thumb">
        <img title="about us" alt="about us" src="images/aboutsckope.jpg" />
       </div>
       <!-- /.sample-thumb -->
      </div>
      <!-- /.widget-item -->
     </div>
     <!-- /.col-md-4 -->
     <div class="col-md-6">
      <!-- second column -->
      <div class="widget-item">
       <h3 class="widget-title">
        Business Principles
       </h3>
       <div class="sample-thumb">
       </div>
       <!-- /.sample-thumb -->
       <p>
        SCKOPEMATE KONSULT LIMITED business principles  are an extension of our values, which enables us to make well informed business  decisions, which influences the way we render services.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        We are positioned to take the second level burden off  our client’s shoulders and get the job done.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        The company believes that securing the right support  services can make all the difference when dealing with project’s critical  timing, cost and performance objectives. SCKOPEMATE KONSULT LIMITED is available to help.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        <span class="widget-title">
        </span>
       </p>
       <h3 class="widget-title">
        MISSION STATEMENT
       </h3>
       <p>
        <span class="widget-title">
        </span>
       </p>
       SCKOPEMATE KONSULT LIMITED mission is to be a trusted and reliable partner in the provision of qualitative services within the West African sub-region, during project concept, engineering design, and construction. These includes consultation and support services to any infrastructural development on land, swamp, near-shore and offshore. 
We set out to achieve this mission through: -
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         - Customer focus attitude
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
         - Provision of high-quality and innovative services.
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
         - Utilization of multi-disciplined professionals and motivated employees
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
         - Functional state-of-art technology and system applications
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
         - Continuous evaluation of our work attitude, principles and method
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
         - Performance of our duties safely and in strictly compliance with optimal industrial standard with due regards to government’s applicable legislation, safety and environmental protection regulatory requirements
        </li>
       </ul>
       <h4 class="consult-title">
       </h4>
